metadata.name: "Subterranean"
metadata.description:
Cynthia DiDonato, “Subterranean” 2018-2022
1/1 NFT Duration: 60 seconds MPEG-4 video
1503x1108px
“Subterranean” is an artistic interpretation of a black hole. How is a black hole created? It forms when the center of a massive star collapses in upon itself.
“Look deep into nature and then you understand everything” Einstein
